                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="age-tips">
                        <p><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> <strong>Why age matters:</strong> Younger skin is more sensitive to UV damage, while older skin needs extra protection and care.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="navigation-buttons">
                    <button class="nav-btn prev" onclick="prevStep()">
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back
                    </button>
                    <button class="nav-btn next" onclick="nextStep()">
