                    <div class="success-animation">
                        <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    </div>

                    <h3>You're All Set! ðŸŽ‰</h3>
                    <p>Your profile has been personalized. We'll use this information to provide you with accurate sun protection advice tailored to your needs.</p>

                    <div class="profile-summary">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i> Your Profile Summary</h4>
                        <div class="summary-grid">
                            <div class="summary-item">
                                <span>Skin Type</span>
                                <strong id="summarySkinType">Not selected</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="summary-item">
                                <span>Skin Condition</span>
                                <strong id="summarySkinCondition">Not selected</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="summary-item">
                                <span>Age</span>
                                <strong id="summaryAge">Not selected</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="summary-item">
                                <span>Cancer History</span>
                                <strong id="summaryCancerHistory">No</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="summary-item">
                                <span>Location</span>
                                <strong id="summaryLocation">Not selected</strong>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="benefits-list">
                        <p><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #10b981;"></i> <strong>What you'll get:</strong></p>
                        <ul style="text-align: left; max-width: 400px; margin: 20px auto; color: #6b7280;">
                            <li>Personalized daily protection plans</li>
                            <li>Real-time UV index monitoring</li>
                            <li>AI-powered clothing recommendations</li>
                            <li>Air quality alerts for your area</li>
                            <li>Skin health tracking over time</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
